OOC: Yep, I chose it, why?

BIC:
Speedbreaker skids to a halt, then quickly transforms, and does a flip
as the momentum of his stop catches up. He lands on his feet, and then
walks through the brush. "Here we are." He announces, showing off the
Decepticon ship.
